Name: Average resolution time of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' cases
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Total duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Median duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' before transitioning to any 'Accepted + In Progress' activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + In Progress'

Name: Average duration from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to 'Completed + Resolved'
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Total time spent in 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities across all cases
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Longest duration of a single 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activity
Metric: the maximum of the duration between the first time instant when `ACTIVITY` == 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the last time instant when <ppinot4py.model.states.RuntimeState object at 0x000001A843391A90> - AppliesTo.PROCESS

Name: Shortest duration of a single 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activity
Metric: The minimum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities during the resolution of incidents
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Resolved'

Name: Distribution of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' durations across different organization countries
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and the end of case grouped by the last value of organization country

Name: Time from the first 'Unmatched + Unmatched' occurrence to the last 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in the log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched'

Name: Average time from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to the next activity in the most frequent process variant
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Total duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities in cases involving 'PROD582'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Average duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities in cases resolved within the same day
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Comparison of average duration between 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and 'Accepted + Wait - User' activities
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Accepted + Wait - User'

Name: Duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities before transitioning to 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Queued + Awaiting Assignment'

Name: Time until resolution from the point of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' in cases with 'Completed + In Call'
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + In Call'

Name: Average duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities in cases exceeding the average resolution time
Metric: The average of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Total cumulative duration of 'Unmatched + Unmatched' activities in the event log
Metric: The sum of the duration between activity Unmatched + Unmatched and the end of the case

Name: Average lead time from 'Unmatched + Unmatched' to case closure
Metric: The average of the duration between activity 'Unmatched + Unmatched' and activity 'Completed + Closed'
